  <brief_title>NC-6004(Nanoplatin) and Gemcitabine to Treat Pancreatic Cancer in Asia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I/II Study of the Combination Therapy With NC-6004 and Gemcitabine in Patients With Locally Advanced or Metastatic Pancreatic Cancer in Asian Countries</official_title>
