  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the recommended dose of NC-6004 according to the
      dose-limiting toxicity (DLT) in combination with Gemcitabine, and to assess the efficacy,
      safety and tolerability.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
