    <description>Nanoplatin (NC-6004) had to be administered once every 3 weeks, on Day 1, Day 22 and Day 43 etc.
Gemcitabine had to be administered to every patient 2 times on Day 1 and Day 8 every 3 weeks after the infusion of Nanoplatin (NC-6004).</description>
